selected_skills.name: analyze_food_web_impact
selected_skills.purpose: To determine the impact of changes in species population on other species within a food web.
selected_skills.how_to_use: Use this skill to analyze the relationship between pelicans and fish and predict the impact on the fish population when the number of pelicans increases.

selected_skills.name: map_count_to_option
selected_skills.purpose: To map a determined effect or count to a multiple-choice option.
selected_skills.how_to_use: Use this skill to map the predicted impact on the fish population to one of the given multiple-choice options.
